data.description: GREAT LOCATION with mountain views, walking, hiking, and bike trails. Easy freeway access is just a minute away. This stunning 3-bed, 3.5-bath END UNIT townhome is in the Bluff View Townhomes Subdivision! Updated flooring, kitchen backsplash, extended driveway & enclosed backyard. Large basement currently used as a theater but can be used as a 4th bedroom. Tranquil and clean family-oriented area. The clubhouse has a pool with a jacuzzi, ideal for small gatherings with a TV room, gym, good sized living room with a fireplace and kitchen! Call listing agent for a showing!
